data.description: Love where you live! If you're searching for a home in a peaceful neighborhood, take a look at this newer construction build situated on a quiet cul-de-sac in Westbrook Estates, which is located in the Tuslaw School District. This spacious four-bedroom house with two and a half baths provides ample space for your entire family. The interior features an open-concept living and kitchen area that's perfect for hosting gatherings. The kitchen is equipped with a large island and plenty of cupboard space for the chef in your family. Additionally, there's a large master bedroom and an ensuite bathroom, ensuring that you'll have a comfortable and private space to unwind. The patio area is perfect for enjoying fall evenings and having a bonfire with friends and family.
